---
title: Vietnamese-Style Beef & Mint Salad with Crushed Peanuts & Sweet Chilli
description: When it starts to heat up outside, we crave something light and fresh. This Vietnamese-inspired salad bowl ticks both those boxes, with a rainbow of fresh veg, golden chunks of beef in a fresh and fragrant sauce, and a sprinkle of crushed peanuts for that all-important crunch. Bring on the warm weather, we’re ready!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 40g carbohydrates per serving.*
